KeysToEntries.story_3_2_001:
Good enough…
let’s get back to
what I was saying…
KeysToEntries.story_3_2_003:
You’ll battle two racers
I have in mind…
KeysToEntries.story_3_2_004:
One of them…
my own younger brother, Keisuke…
KeysToEntries.story_3_2_005:
And the other is…
the man called
Akina’s 86…
